author: Stoekken, Christian von, 1633-1684
title: Animæ damnatæ lamenta et tormenta rhythmis non inconcinnis anonymo authore ante seculum, & quod excurrit, expressa, quibus subjunguntur rhythmi de extremo judicio & trinitatis mysterio, quos emendatos & ad orthodoxiam reformatos in vernaculam eodem rhythm
